<h3>Precipitation</h3>
<br><br>
The precipitation in May was (exceptionally) much below average in Southwest Europe and the western part of Europe, and (exceptionally) much above average in the northern and easter parts of Europe (figure 9). In parts of Spain there was no precipitation at all (Figure 8).
